  <summary date="2020-06-16T17:56:01Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Nationwide Right To Unionize Act

This bill provides authorization for labor agreements to require membership in a labor organization as a condition of employment regardless of state law (thus preempting state laws that prohibit such agreements).</summary>
